| Feature                     | Description                                                     |
| --------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------- |
| ✅ **Self-healing**          | Automatically stops bad EC2 and picks another stopped one.      |
| ✅ **SSH readiness check**   | Waits up to 5 min for port 22 before declaring failure.         |
| ✅ **Logging clarity**       | Every step logs `[INFO]`, `[WARN]`, `[ERROR]`, `[CRITICAL]`.    |
| ✅ **Fallback pool logic**   | If 1 master or slave fails, picks another from remaining list.  |
| ✅ **`summary.json` output** | Shows which nodes started, failed, replaced.                    |
| ✅ **Backward compatible**   | `instance_info.json` stays same — no pipeline changes required. |
